			<div class="et_pb_slide et_pb_slide_6 et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_media_alignment_center">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_container clearfix">
					<div class="et_pb_slider_container_inner">
						
						<div class="et_pb_slide_description">
							<h2 class="et_pb_slide_title">7 of 13</h2>
				<div class="et_pb_slide_content"><p>&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">A former building commissioner reflects on the decision to build the Sears Tower. Click the play button to listen to this audio clip.</p>
<p style="text-align: right;">
<!-- iframe plugin v.4.3 wordpress.org/plugins/iframe/ -->
<iframe width="420" height="315" src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/Z5opKUQqsLA" frameborder="0" allow="autoplay; encrypted-media" 0="allowfullscreen" scrolling="yes" class="iframe-class"></iframe>
</p>
<p style="text-align: right;"><em>Audio: Joseph Fitzgerald, Chicago Building Commissioner, interview excerpt, July 24, 2014</em></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><div id="attachment_1948" style="width: 310px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><a href="https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2015/05/RJD_06_01_0041_0008_001a.jpg" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img class="wp-image-1948 size-medium" src="https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2015/05/RJD_06_01_0041_0008_001a-300x300.jpg" alt="Medallion--Sears Tower, 1973 &#091;front&#093;. RJD_06_01_0041_0008_001a " width="300" height="300" srcset="https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2015/05/RJD_06_01_0041_0008_001a-300x300.jpg 300w, https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2015/05/RJD_06_01_0041_0008_001a-150x150.jpg 150w, https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2015/05/RJD_06_01_0041_0008_001a-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2015/05/RJD_06_01_0041_0008_001a-1080x1080.jpg 1080w, https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2015/05/RJD_06_01_0041_0008_001a.jpg 1500w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">Medallion&#8211;Sears Tower, 1973 [front]. RJD_06_01_0041_0008_001a</p></div><div id="attachment_1949" style="width: 310px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><a href="https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2015/05/RJD_06_01_0041_0008_001b.jpg" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img class="wp-image-1949 size-medium" src="https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2015/05/RJD_06_01_0041_0008_001b-300x300.jpg" alt="Medallion--Sears Tower, 1973 &#091;back&#093;. RJD_06_01_0041_0008_001b" width="300" height="300" srcset="https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2015/05/RJD_06_01_0041_0008_001b-300x300.jpg 300w, https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2015/05/RJD_06_01_0041_0008_001b-150x150.jpg 150w, https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2015/05/RJD_06_01_0041_0008_001b-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/si