							<h2 class="et_pb_slide_title">8 of 13</h2>
				<div class="et_pb_slide_content"><div id="attachment_976" style="width: 882px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><a href="https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2015/05/RJD_04_01_0031_0016_001.jpg" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img class="wp-image-976" src="https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2015/05/RJD_04_01_0031_0016_001-1024x706.jpg" alt="Richard J. Daley visits the 1500 block of West Jackson for an urban renewal project" width="872" height="601" srcset="https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2015/05/RJD_04_01_0031_0016_001-1024x706.jpg 1024w, https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2015/05/RJD_04_01_0031_0016_001-300x207.jpg 300w, https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2015/05/RJD_04_01_0031_0016_001-1080x744.jpg 1080w, https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2015/05/RJD_04_01_0031_0016_001.jpg 1500w" sizes="(max-width: 872px) 100vw, 872px" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">Richard J. Daley visits the 1500 block of West Jackson for an urban renewal project, ca. 1970s. RJD_4_01_0031_0016_001</p></div>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<div id="attachment_965" style="width: 848px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><a href="https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2015/05/RJD_04_01_0017_0001_016.jpg" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img class="wp-image-965" src="https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2015/05/RJD_04_01_0017_0001_016-1024x805.jpg" alt="Richard J. Daley at new county jail site" width="838" height="659" srcset="https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2015/05/RJD_04_01_0017_0001_016-1024x805.jpg 1024w, https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2015/05/RJD_04_01_0017_0001_016-300x236.jpg 300w, https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2015/05/RJD_04_01_0017_0001_016-1080x849.jpg 1080w, https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2015/05/RJD_04_01_0017_0001_016.jpg 1500w" sizes="(max-width: 838px) 100vw, 838px" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">Richard J. Daley at new county jail site, ca. 1960s. RJD_04_01_0017_0001_016</p></div></div>
							
