						<div class="et_pb_slide_description">
							<h2 class="et_pb_slide_title">9 of 13</h2>
				<div class="et_pb_slide_content"><div id="attachment_962" style="width: 1034px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><a href="https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2015/05/RJD_04_01_0014_0004_003.jpg" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img class="wp-image-962 size-large" src="https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2015/05/RJD_04_01_0014_0004_003-1024x806.jpg" alt="Crawford Parker (Indiana's lieutenant governor), and Richard J. Daley lift the barricades to through traffic on the Calumet Skyway, April 16, 1958. RJD_04_01_0014_0004_003" width="1024" height="806" srcset="https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2015/05/RJD_04_01_0014_0004_003-1024x806.jpg 1024w, https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2015/05/RJD_04_01_0014_0004_003-300x236.jpg 300w, https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2015/05/RJD_04_01_0014_0004_003-1080x850.jpg 1080w, https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2015/05/RJD_04_01_0014_0004_003.jpg 1500w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">Crawford Parker (Indiana&#8217;s lieutenant governor), and Richard J. Daley lift the barricades to through traffic on the Calumet Skyway, April 16, 1958. RJD_04_01_0014_0004_003</p></div></div>
							
