								City Beautiful, City Cultural							</a>
						</h2>
					

											<p class="post-meta">
							<a href="https://rjd.library.uic.edu/project_category/citythatworks/" title="City That Works">City That Works</a>						</p>
					
				</div><!-- .et_pb_portfolio_item -->
								<div id="post-413" class="post-413 project type-project status-publish has-post-thumbnail hentry project_category-citythatworks et_pb_post et_pb_portfolio_item et_pb_grid_item">

										<a href="https://rjd.library.uic.edu/a-union-man-a-business-mayor/" title="A Union Man, A Business Mayor">
													<span class="et_portfolio_image">
								<img src="https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2015/05/RJD_04_01_0029_0004_002-400x284.jpg" alt="A Union Man, A Business Mayor" width="400" height="284" />
								<span class="et_overlay"></span>							</span>
											</a>
					
											<h2 class="et_pb_module_header">
							<a href="https://rjd.library.uic.edu/a-union-man-a-business-mayor/" title="A Union Man, A Business Mayor">
